These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-1::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: emerald, mauve, ebony, grey, white
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, ship, snowmobile, van
 1. the person who likes white is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
 2. the person who likes emerald is the person driving the motorbike##1
 3. the person driving the motorbike is the person who likes emerald##1
 4. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the right of the person driving the van##5
 5. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 6. the person who likes white is not to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##8
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
 8. the person who likes white is not the person driving the ship##6
 9. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person who likes mauve##3
10. the person driving the boat is not the person who likes grey##6
11. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1
12. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
13. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8
14. the person who likes ebony is somewhere between the person who likes white and the person driving the ship##7
15. the person who likes emerald is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |     4      |     5     |
| Color        | mauve | ebony | white | grey     | emerald    |
| Transport   | ship | van       | boat   | snowmobile | motorbike |

