.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-2::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, iced-tea, mirinda, 7up
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, brazilian, british, malaysian, thai
 1. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
 2. the thai is not to the left of the argentine##8
 3. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the british##5
 4. the argentine is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
 5. the person drinking 7up is not to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
 6. the brazilian is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6
 7. the argentine is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the malaysian is on the left of the thai##1
 9. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
10. the person drinking 7up is not to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |     4     |    5    |
| Beverage   | mirinda | 7up    | hot-chocolate | lemonade  | iced-tea |
| Nationality   | argentine  | malaysian | thai      | brazilian | british |

