.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-3::.
There are 5 different nationalities: japanese, turkish, german, spanish, indian
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, folk, house, indie
1. the japanese is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
2. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
3. the turkish is between the fan of house and the spanish##2
4. the turkish is the fan of folk##1
5. the indian is in the middle##1
6. the japanese is on the left of the fan of classical##1
7. the japanese is not to the left of the indian##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |       3        |     4     |     5     |
| Nationality           | spanish | turkish | indian | japanese | german  |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep  | folk        | house          | indie     | classical |

