.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-6::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, iced-tea, lemonade, tea
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, august, october, april, september
 1. the person drinking lemonade is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##8
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the left of the person drinking lemonade##8
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in september and the person drinking almond-milk##7
 6. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking lemonade##7
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking tea##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##8
10. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
11. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
12. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| Beverage    | iced-tea | lemonade | tea     | almond-milk | coffee |
| Birthday   | october    | september    | august | january         | april   |

