.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-7::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: train, ship, tram, boat, scooter
5 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, fish, frog, mouse
 1. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5
 2. the owner of the frog is not to the left of the person driving the scooter##8
 3. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 4. the owner of the ferret is somewhere between the owner of the cat and the owner of the frog##7
 5. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
 6. the owner of the cat is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8
 7. the owner of the frog is not the person driving the train##6
 8. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
 9. the person driving the boat is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8
10. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
11. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
12. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5
13. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |   3    |   4    |     5     |
| Transport   | tram | ship | boat | scooter | train |
| Pet           | mouse     | cat       | ferret | frog   | fish      |

