.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-8::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: drama, epic, fantasy, horror, western
House: futuristic, townhouse, colonial, tower, art-deco
 1. the townhouse house is not the person watching western movies##6
 2. the tower house is in the middle##1
 3. the person watching western movies is not to the left of the townhouse house##8
 4. the townhouse house is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5
 5. the person watching drama movies is not to the left of the colonial house##8
 6. the futuristic house is somewhere to the left of the art-deco house##5
 7. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person watching horror movies is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person watching drama movies is somewhere between the colonial house and the futuristic house##7
10. the colonial house is in an odd position##4
11. the person watching drama movies is not the futuristic house##6
12. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |  4   |    5    |
| Movie-Genre   | horror    | drama      | western | epic | fantasy |
| House     | colonial | townhouse | tower    | futuristic  | art-deco  |

