.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-9::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, may, july, august, october
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, disaster, family, romance
 1. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 2. the person watching family movies is not to the left of the person watching romance movies##8
 3. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
 4. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 5. the person watching family movies is not to the left of the person watching romance movies##8
 6. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##5
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
10. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4     |      5      |
| Birthday           | october | february | august | may   | july |
| Movie-Genre   | crime     | romance  | family     | disaster | adventure   |

