 4. the brazilian is somewhere to the right of the french##5
 5. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the person eating onion##5
 6. the thai is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the french is in an odd position##4
 8. the person eating raspberry is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
 9. the person eating raspberry is not the thai##6
