6. the person eating raspberry is not to the right of the person driving the skateboard##8
7. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
8. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |
