 3. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the left of the person who likes fuchsia##8
 4. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 5. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person who likes fuchsia##5
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the person who likes grey##8
 7. the person who likes amber is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
 8. the person who likes aquamarine is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8
 9. the person who likes ebony is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
10. the person drinking tea is not to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
11. the person who likes ebony is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
12. the person drinking milk is between the person who likes fuchsia and the person who likes grey##2

.:: Answer ::.
