 9. the person drinking coffee is not the person who's hobby is cooking##6
10. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's hobby is chess##1
12. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
13. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not the person who's hobby is fishing##6
14. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
